  calories: 870 kcal
  fat: 20 g
  saturated fat: 3 g
  carbohydrates: 131 g
  sugar: 55 g
  protein: 38 g
  fiber: 4 g
  sodium: 2550 mg
servings: 2
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/orange-chicken-6182a287ed9d7726956e4fbf
time required: 45 minutes
cuisine: Asian
author: Sara Heilman
